    )
    (symbol "?!_0CMOS_1_1"
      (text "\"0CMOS\" library. rev 2.0\n\n在 KiCAD 中使用 Virtuoso 风格的 CMOS 器件符号.\n0CMOS 的名称使其在库列表中置顶, 并避免与内置库冲突.\n二极管、电容、电阻等请用 Device 内置库中的器件.\n栅格间距请使用 50mils (1.27mm)，KiCAD 版本至少为 7.0.\n\nLast Mod: adq @ xjtu 260610\n\nContents:\n\nFETs:\n\nNM*, PM*\n4T = with backgate\nISO = with ISO/ISUB connections\nBS = B-S shorted\nHV, LD = DEMOS, LDMOS\nNA = native / lvt / depletion\nT = HV gate / hvt\n\nNFET, PFET\nNJFET, PJFET\nNPN, _Alt, _S\nPNP, _Alt\n\nD_Filled_ISO" (at 0 -2.54 0)
        (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
      )
      (text "analog blocks:\n\nCOMP, _CLK, _Schmitt\nOPA, _Diff, _Diff_Alt, _Diff_CM\nOTA, _Alt\nSW, SW_1, SW_2, SW_Chop, SW_Chop_P, SW_Dual, SW_Small\nMUX2, MUX5\n\n\nmisc blocks:\n\nBlock, Block2, _Edge, _Oneshot, _OneshotEdge,\n_OSC, _OSC_Ctrl, _Ramp, _Sum\nDAC (also as ADC)\nPort\nWireStop, WireStop_Bus\n\n\nlogics:\n\nINV, _3state, _Delay, _Schmitt\nBUF, _3state, _Delay, _Schmitt, _Diff, _Diff_O, _Diff_I, BUF_LS\nAND, AND3, NAND, NAND3\nOR, OR3, NOR, NOR3\nXOR, XNOR\nD_FF, D_FF_nR, D_FF_nRnS, D_Latch\nJK_FF_nRnS\nRS_Latch_NAND, RS_Latch_NOR\n\n\nsources:\n\nidc, _Alt, _Trim\nvdc, _Trim\n\n\neditable power symbols, copied from power lib:\n\npower-GND, power-VDD, power-VSS\npower-GNDD, power-GNDPWR, power-GNDREF" (at 63.5 -2.54 0)
        (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
      )
    )
  )
